Title: Refundable Core Charge
meta_title: Refundable Core Charge for Vintage & Classic Mopar Parts
meta_description: Understand the refundable core charge policy for Chrysler, DeSoto, Dodge, and Plymouth auto parts. Learn how the charge ensures part quality.
product_description: The refundable core charge is an integral part of the auto parts purchasing process for vintage and classic Mopar cars, including Chrysler, DeSoto, Dodge, and Plymouth. Essentially, this charge is a deposit ensuring that the old part is returned in exchange for a refurbished or new one. Once you return your old part, you get this core charge refunded. It's a great system that guarantees the availability of quality parts and supports recycling efforts. For any further questions or assistance, feel free to ask!
